        <h2>Traditional Wedding in Andhra Pradesh</h2>
        <p>
            A traditional Andhra wedding is a grand celebration of customs, rituals, and cultural values, steeped in deep spiritual significance. These weddings reflect the rich heritage of Andhra Pradesh, blending joy, devotion, and familial warmth in a series of vibrant ceremonies.
        </p>
        <h3>Pre-Wedding Rituals: Setting the Stage</h3>
