                The bride and groom take a sacred bath early in the morning, marking purification for the holy event.
            <b>2.Gauri Pooja:</b>
                The bride prays to Goddess Gauri, seeking blessings for a happy and prosperous marriage.
            <b>3.Ganesh Pooja:</b>
                The groom offers prayers to Lord Ganesha to remove obstacles and bless the couple’s new journey.
